{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":18266,"name":"","username":"slapin","avatar_template":"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/s/dfb087/{size}.png","created_at":"2017-06-01T00:22:05.236Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eHi, all\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease see the bug:\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003caside class=\"onebox githubissue\"\u003e\n  \u003cheader class=\"source\"\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/issues/1961\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003egithub.com/urho3d/Urho3D\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003c/header\u003e\n  \u003carticle class=\"onebox-body\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/slapin\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\n\u003cimg src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/6099?v=2\u0026amp;s=96\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"420\" height=\"420\"\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/issues/1961\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eIssue: Node-\u0026gt;LookAt as well as FromLookRotation reverse direction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"date\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv class=\"user\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"\u003e\n\topened by \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/slapin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eslapin\u003c/a\u003e\n\ton \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/issues/1961\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e2017-05-27\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv class=\"user\"\u003e\n\tclosed by \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/weitjong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eweitjong\u003c/a\u003e\n\ton \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/issues/1961\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e2017-06-03\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cpre class=\"content\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eIf one uses Node-\u0026gt;LookAt() of quat.FromLookRotation() they find-out that both node and quat\nlook in reverse direction from what it was intended...\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"labels\"\u003e\n \t\u003cspan style=\"display:inline-block;margin-top:2px;background-color: #B8B8B8;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;color: #fff;margin-left: 3px;\"\u003ewontfix\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/article\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"onebox-metadata\"\u003e\n    \n    \n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"clear: both\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis bug is show stopper for my project.\u003cbr\u003e\nThis one hit me so badly so I suspended all farther work with Urho for now.\u003cbr\u003e\nLooking forward for the fix. Will provide any details necessary to fix this one.\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-06-01T00:22:05.236Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":73,"reads":44,"readers_count":43,"score":373.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":3183,"topic_slug":"headsup-world-rotations-are-completely-broken-with-urho","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/issues/1961","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"Node-\u003eLookAt as well as FromLookRotation reverse direction · Issue #1961 · urho3d/Urho3D · GitHub","clicks":16},{"url":"https://github.com/slapin","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"slapin (Sergey Lapin) · GitHub","clicks":0},{"url":"https://github.com/weitjong","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"weitjong (Yao Wei Tjong) · GitHub","clicks":0}],"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":554,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"w